pageProduct.name: Swisse Men's Ultivite Multivitamin 120 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultivite Men's Multivitamin is a premium quality formula containing 52 vitamins, minerals, antioxidants and herbs tailored for men. It supports healthy stress response in the body, maintains energy production, stamina and vitality, and supports cognitive function.

Size: 120 Tablets

Warnings

Vitamin & mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. This product contains selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150 mcg for adults of selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. Not for the treatment of iron deficiency conditions.

Ingredients

Each tablet contains: Biotin 50 mcg; Choline Bitartrate 25 mg; Folic Acid 500 mcg; Nicotinamide 30 mg; Vitamin B1 (thiamine hydrochloride) 30.93 mg; Vitamin B2 (riboflavin) 30 mg; Vitamin B5 (pantothenic acid from calcium pantothenate) 64.13 mg; Vitamin B6 (pyridoxine from pyridoxine hydrochloride) 24.68 mg; Vitamin B12 (cyanocobalamin) 30 mcg; Vitamin C (ascorbic acid from calcium ascorbate dihydrate) 165.2 mg; Vitamin D3 (colecalciferol) 5 mcg; Vitamin E (d-alpha-tocopheryl acid succinate) 41.33 mg; Calcium (from calcium citrate tetrahydrate) 21 mg; Chromium (from chromium picolinate) 6.2 mcg; Copper (from copper gluconate) 28 mcg; Iodine (from potassium iodide) 50 mcg; Iron (from ferrous fumarate) 3 mg; Magnesium (from heavy magnesium oxide) 57.89 mg; Manganese (from manganese amino acid chelate) 1.2 mg; Potassium (from potassium sulfate) 4 mg; Selenium (from selenomethionine) 26 mcg; Zinc (from zinc amino acid chelate) 6 mg; Betacarotene 5 mg; Citrus Bioflavonoids Extract 40 mg; Co-enzyme Q10 (ubidecarenone) 1 mg; Inositol 25 mg; Lutein 200 mcg; Lysine Hydrochloride 50 mg; Tyrosine 1 mg; Astragalus (Astragalus membranaceus extract 5 mg) equiv. dry root 50 mg; Barberry (Berberis vulgaris extract 2.5 mg) equiv. dry root bark 15 mg; Bilberry (Vaccinium myrtillus extract 250 mcg) equiv. fresh fruit 25 mg; Buchu (Agathosma betulina extract 2.5 mg) equiv. dry leaf 10 mg; Celery (Apium graveolens extract 1.6 mg) equiv. dry seed 20 mg; Fennel (Foeniculum vulgare extract 3 mg) equiv. dry fruit 15 mg; Ginger (Zingiber officinale extract 1 mg) equiv. dry rhizome 5 mg; Ginkgo (Ginkgo biloba extract 2 mg) equiv. dry leaf 100 mg; Globe Artichoke (Cynara scolymus extract 12.5 mg) equiv. dry leaf 50 mg; Gotu Kola (Centella asiatica extract 12.5 mg) equiv. dry whole plant 50 mg; Grape Seed (Vitis vinifera extract 9.9 mg) equiv. dry seed 1.19 g; Green Tea (Camellia sinensis extract 3.34 mg) equiv. dry leaf 20 mg; Hawthorn (Crataegus monogyna extract 20 mg) equiv. dry fruit 100 mg; Horsetail (Equisetum arvense extract 7.5 mg) equiv. dry herb 30 mg; Korean Ginseng (Panax ginseng extract 16.67 mg) equiv. dry root 50 mg; Milk Thistle (Silybum marianum extract 714 mcg) equiv. dry fruit 50 mg; Oats (Avena sativa extract 50 mg) equiv. dry herb 500 mg; Papaya (Carica papaya dry fruit powder) 10 mg; Parsley (Petroselinum crispum extract 2.5 mg) equiv. dry herb 10 mg; Sarsaparilla (Smilax officinalis extract 12.5 mg) equiv. dry root 68.75 mg; Saw Palmetto (Serenoa repens extract 20 mg) equiv. dry fruit 200 mg; Spearmint Oil 1.5 mg; Tomato (Lycopersicon esculentum extract 2 mg) equiv. fresh fruit 700 mg.

Directions

Adult Dosage: One tablet daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place.
